title: #92Noon! Friday Football Feast! House/Simpson
description: Nordo and Charch are at the Fair for the Friday Football Feast! Charch gives a history lesson on AP, Daniel House joins to talk Gophers ahead of their matchup with the Buckeyes, local artist Mae Simpson talks her career and her style of music.
